{"tid":1691641,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"求下和理非們可憐下勇武們代佢哋入差館坐48粒鐘","createTime":"2019-11-03T17:46:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-17T12:15:17.000Z","uid":303608,"like":23,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"e845e7e172eeb1a8b869cf9bbd5cbe07d45e7268","tid":1691641,"uid":303608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T17:46:05.000Z","msg":"唔係譴責唔係割蓆唔係分化<br />\n但都咁多個月了 和理非可唔可以為勇武手足做多少少犧牲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n勇武撤嘅時候 比條路勇武湧入你哋成大班人入面<br />\n求下你哋見到勇武走 唔好跟住走 可唔可以保護一下佢哋<br />\n比佢哋走咗先 你哋再走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你哋比狗咬最多坐48粒鐘 勇武們係幾年十碌甚至終身(火魔法師)架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n得黑衫無gear佢告你非法集結你都可以輕鬆踢保 見到狗衝緊埋嚟覺得不妙可以除罩先 咁又少條罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n求下你哋 保護下勇武 勇武無就無架啦 唔係求你哋同勇武手足一樣咁大勇氣上前線 只係想你哋用自己嘅48粒鐘 換佢哋嘅幾十年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n和理非們可唔可以答應我唔好再見到狗就走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n的起心肝唔好再指意勇武保護自己 而係你哋保護勇武<br />\n啲狗鳩拉你佢哋都吹你唔漲架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n求下你哋啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我唔想再有手足為依個政權白白咁坐監呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e6a27addb70c4a08f270db99b00c6ef47b8457d","tid":1691641,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T17:59:29.000Z","msg":"甴近平<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[日常文宣] [文宣方向] 以子之矛，攻子之盾<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1691650\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1691650</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"3db59a44e02746f3bcb727a49544da4fb0c3d89e","tid":1691641,"uid":61160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T18:15:13.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"7